<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Fragment from a<rs type="material"> white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">panel</rs> perhaps with back but no edges (<measure precision="circa" type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.19</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.29</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.09</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face which is worn, perhaps by water.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Standard second to third century forms; no measurements.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0201" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Probably third century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">nomenclature</rs>)
</p>
</div>
